  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 7th level, the darkness that clouds other shinobi in fear and mystery becomes your ally in your righteous endevors.</p><p>You gain 20 feet of blindsight and have advantage on Perception checks to locate creatures attempting to hide from you using darkness of any kind, of any source.</p><p>Additionally, while you are in a lightly obscured (Dim Light), you gain a +2 to to unarmed, Taijutsu, and Gadget attack rolls.</p><p>If you are instead in total darkness or a heavily obscured area, you instead gain advantage.</p><p></p>",
